data.description: Welcome home to this magnificent opportunity to own in the gated community of Bermuda Springs in the greatly desired area of Weston. This charming single-family residence features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with an open floor layout and many upgrades throughout.  NEW ROOF 2023. Tankless WH 2017. Updated kitchen and flooring throughtout the home.  Walking distance from shops, schools, restaurants and parks.  Community pool and has one of the lowest HOA fees in Weston.  Orignal Owner/ One owner. Realtor related to seller/owner
